# Predictive Modeling Using Machine Learning

## Objective
Build a machine learning model to predict restaurant ratings.

## Libraries Used
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib

## Algorithm Used
- Linear Regression

## Features
- Data preprocessing
- Label Encoding
- Train-test split
- Model training
- Rating prediction
- Model evaluation

## Evaluation Metrics
- Mean Squared Error
- R2 Score

## Visualization
- Actual vs Predicted Ratings graph